fields.title: Jewellery box with Henna designs and Rhinestones. Perfect as Bridesmaid Gift/Wedding Gift/Jewellery Storage
fields.description:
These wooden boxes are spray painted and then hand painted with henna designs on them making them unique. Rhinestones adds a perfect sparkle to them.It has velvet lining inside for a softer feel.

They would make a perfect gift for a wedding or bridesmaids.
Boxes can be customized to any color and stones.

Dimensions :
Length :8.5"
Width :5.25"
Height : 3.5"

Each box is uniquely painted. I try to ship them as early as possible, but sometimes can take anywhere from 1-2 weeks. For special occasion orders above $150 please do contact me early so that I could ship them on time.

Returns/Refunds/Exchange: I do accept returns in original condition or if it arrives damaged.Return shipping paid by customer.
Contact me within 1 week of delivery.
Request a cancellation within 2 days of purchase.
